                    <h3>Line by Line (Preferred)</h3>
                    <pre><code class="python"># Efficient for big files
with open("data.txt", "r") as f:
    for line in f:
        print(line.strip())</code></pre>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Read All Lines</h3>
                    <pre><code class="python"># Loads entire file into a list
with open("data.txt", "r") as f:
